<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Manhattan Institute</ENAMEX> meeting, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Lawrence B. Lindsey</ENAMEX>, a leading supply-side
flag-waver in the <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Reagan</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Treasury Department</ENAMEX> (now a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">governor</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Federal</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Reserve</ENAMEX>) whipped out a graph (see above/below) to show that tax revenues in
